  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "chapterTitle": "3.4 科学方法",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26454161_16_731-910",
          "range": "731-910",
          "rangeStart": 731,
          "rangeEnd": 910,
          "markText": "不过，我们必须记住，即便是科学，其自身也有限制，且科学并不是真相的化身，这点很重要。实际上，科学是：\n1. 有时效性的；\n2. 有前提条件的；\n3. 我们目前所能做出的最大努力。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1717028808,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-30 08:26:48",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=731&rangeEnd=910",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=731&rangeEnd=910"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_4_391-485",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "391-485",
      "markText": "这本指南不是我写的，我只是发现了它。此前，它一直藏在岩石里。而我之所以知道这件事是因为，我就是把那块厚重的变质岩敲开的人。为了做成这件事，我在工地上干了几个星期，因为我听说这活儿回报丰厚。",
      "totalCount": 675,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=391&rangeEnd=485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=391&rangeEnd=485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_22_28532-28631",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "28532-28631",
      "markText": "蚊子是少数几种尽数消灭不会对地球产生任何负面效果的动物之一：它们在生态系统中扮演的角色（作为鸟类的食物，进行少量的授粉工作）已经被其他昆虫取代了。它们灭绝后，唯一的结果是：死于疟疾的人类会越来越少。",
      "totalCount": 594,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=28532&rangeEnd=28631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=28532&rangeEnd=28631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_7_666-703",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "666-703",
      "markText": "都会创造一条新的“时间线”，或者说创造过去某个时间点开始发生的一系列事件。",
      "totalCount": 590,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=666&rangeEnd=703",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=666&rangeEnd=703"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_8_389-513",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "389-513",
      "markText": "FC3000TM时光机内部没有用户自维修部件。 FC3000TM时光机无法修理。",
      "totalCount": 520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=389&rangeEnd=513",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=389&rangeEnd=513"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_16_3950-4057",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3950-4057",
      "markText": "人们总是觉得科学家是书呆子，但科学的哲学基础其实更像叛逆又个性化的朋克族：从不迷信权威，从不把任何人对任何事的评价当真，总会自行证实或证伪自以为正确的所有理论。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3950&rangeEnd=4057",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3950&rangeEnd=4057"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_21_11861-11898",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "11861-11898",
      "markText": "土豆是少有的几种含有人类所需全部营养物质的植物之一！你可以完全依靠土豆过活",
      "totalCount": 481,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=11861&rangeEnd=11898",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=11861&rangeEnd=11898"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_8_1017-1029",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1017-1029",
      "markText": "我们诚邀您自行创造未来。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1017&rangeEnd=1029",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1017&rangeEnd=1029"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_13_1707-1727",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1707-1727",
      "markText": "语言是我们编制的，而且是我们随意编制的。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1707&rangeEnd=1727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1707&rangeEnd=1727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_26_20130-20146",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "20130-20146",
      "markText": "不要相信面包是素食产品这种鬼话。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=20130&rangeEnd=20146",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=20130&rangeEnd=20146"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_4_964-1013",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "964-1013",
      "markText": "我们所在的整个宇宙不过是在过去的某个未知时间点上从原初宇宙中剥离出来的一个副本，尽管可能性也不大。",
      "totalCount": 364,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=964&rangeEnd=1013",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=964&rangeEnd=1013"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_7_4048-4085",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4048-4085",
      "markText": "我们的研发团队中有几位伦理学家，他们斩钉截铁地向我们保证，这完全没有问题。",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4048&rangeEnd=4085",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4048&rangeEnd=4085"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_11_2206-2245",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2206-2245",
      "markText": "如果没有语言的支持，这些复杂的想法也无法在头脑中如常涌现，甚至根本不可能出现。",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2245",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2245"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_17_1089-1189",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "1089-1189",
      "markText": "由于你不确定自己究竟会在某个地方待多久，你就不会去建造那些成本高昂且要耗费巨大人力的基础设施。不能随身携带的任何东西都会在一夜之间变为无用之物。你也不会储存任何长期资源，因为根本就没有“长期”这一说。",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1089&rangeEnd=1189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1089&rangeEnd=1189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_5_398-511",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "398-511",
      "markText": "忘记过去的人，注定重蹈覆辙。 ——哲学家、文学批评家、诗人乔治·桑塔亚纳",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=398&rangeEnd=511",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=398&rangeEnd=511"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_13_3150-3270",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3150-3270",
      "markText": "你有机会修正和完善这些语言。不喜欢英语的代词系统？不喜欢法语要赋予万事万物一个虚拟性别的刻板规则？好，现在和这些规则永别的机会来了。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3150&rangeEnd=3270",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3150&rangeEnd=3270"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_11_2688-2739",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2688-2739",
      "markText": "文明进步贴士：语言是一门技术，是后续一切文明发展的基础，而你现在已经免费习得了这门技术。",
      "totalCount": 338,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2688&rangeEnd=2739",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2688&rangeEnd=2739"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_7_1651-1727",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1651-1727",
      "markText": "简单地说，哪怕时间旅行者在回到过去旅行时，胡作非为到了令人发指的程度，也只会影响时间旅行所创造的那条新时间线上的世界，而不会影响我们现在所处的这个世界。",
      "totalCount": 325,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1651&rangeEnd=1727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1651&rangeEnd=1727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_11_1307-1365",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1307-1365",
      "markText": "我们可以做个实验来验证这件事。把你的骨架和20万年前晚期智人的骨架放在一起，你会发现，你根本没有办法将它们区分开来。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_7_2388-2430",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2388-2430",
      "markText": "您给出的彩票中奖号码只会让另一条时间线上的您受益，而不是严格意义上这条时间线上的您。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2388&rangeEnd=2430",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2388&rangeEnd=2430"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26454161_7_1221-1341",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1221-1341",
      "markText": "当您踏上归途、返回现在时，FC3000TM时光机就会穿越空间、时间以及时间线，把您带回我们现在所处的这个世界，历史并不会发生改变。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26454161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1221&rangeEnd=1341",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7532f907193a891f7581b9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1221&rangeEnd=1341"
    }
